# outbound-feed-monitor environment variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values.
# Never commit .env to version control.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Gmail OAuth
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# No env vars needed for Gmail — authentication uses:
#   credentials.json  (downloaded from Google Cloud Console — see README)
#   token.json        (auto-generated on first run, auto-refreshed)
#
# Place credentials.json in the project root before running monitor.py.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Slack Bot Token (Phase 2)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-your-token-here
#
# Required scopes: chat:write, chat:write.public
# See README for step-by-step Slack App creation guide.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Jira API Token (Phase 2)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# JIRA_EMAIL=your.name@example.com
# JIRA_API_TOKEN=your-api-token-here
#
# Generate at: https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens
